Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That you all fear~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:56.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shall unveil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the full moon shall appear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:02.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Over the night sky her voice had rised
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:05.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Slender and gentle still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:09.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now that she's summoning all despised
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shall our dreams fulfill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I shall cast my spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:28.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Summon you under my silk-linen banners
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:35.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Come, little children, my minions, be true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:39.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll reward you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:42.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After my manner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Full moon, the legend's been true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It hangs in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Full moon is calling for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:57.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Won't you reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Full moon, the legend's been true
