Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:31.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wings of a bat and these amber eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Somehow we had to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For rushing in thunder through moonlit skies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Riding the hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:49.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You, once common pegasi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shall be the soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of my nocturne army
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:04.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cast now aside all your fears~ and fly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:11.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Preceding the tidal wave my midnight's bringing on them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who will regret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What we must leave behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And forget and forsake what we loved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:27.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To become ones who ever will trail her the way?
